title: NBA Player Detection/Tracking
description: Detects and tracks players, referees, basketballs, and movement statistics in a video using YOLO and OpenCV. Assigned players to teams based on jersey color using K-means for pixel segmentation and clustering.

title: Real Estate Data Visualization
description: Leveraged AWS Athena and housing data to write Spark SQL queries and create Matplotlib Visualizations. Utilized AWS S3 buckets for data and output, AWS Glue for Database and Table creation, and Athena for queries
